com.drgarbage.bytecode.instructions

Class PaddedInstruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.drgarbage.bytecode.instructions.AbstractInstruction
      • com.drgarbage.bytecode.instructions.PaddedInstruction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Opcodes
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LookupSwitchInstruction, TableSwitchInstruction

    public class PaddedInstruction
extends AbstractInstruction
    Base class for intstructions which need a four byte padding relative to the start of the enclosing code of the parent Code attribute before reading immediate arguments.
    Version:
    $Revision:395 $ $Id:PaddedInstruction.java 395 2008-04-03 15:08:14Z Peter Palaga $
    Author:
    Sergej Alekseev and Peter Palaga
